                        {/* Γ£à CHß╗ê hiß╗ân thß╗ï card Giao h├áng ß╗ƒ chß║┐ ─æß╗Ö Tß║áO ─æ╞ín h├áng, KH├öNG hiß╗ân thß╗ï ß╗ƒ chß║┐ ─æß╗Ö Sß╗¼A */}
                        <ShippingCard hidden={isEditing} />
                    </div>
                </ScrollArea>
                <ProductSelectionDialog 
                    isOpen={isProductSelectionOpen}
