        // 5. Tß║ío phiß║┐u chi cho Ph├¡ vß║¡n chuyß╗ân v├á Chi ph├¡ kh├íc (Trß║ú b├¬n thß╗⌐ 3)
        if (currentShippingFees.length > 0 || currentOtherFees.length > 0) {
