          </div>
        </CardContent>
      </Card>
      
      {/* Info Card */}
      <Card>
        <CardHeader>
          <CardTitle className="text-lg">H╞░ß╗¢ng dß║½n c├ái ─æß║╖t</CardTitle>
        </CardHeader>
        <CardContent className="space-y-3 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
          <p>
            <strong>1.</strong> Trendtech cß║ºn c├│ c├íc API endpoints tß║íi <code>/api/hrm/*</code>
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>2.</strong> API endpoints cß║ºn thiß║┐t:
          </p>
          <ul className="list-disc list-inside ml-4 space-y-1">
            <li><code>GET /api/hrm/ping</code> - Kiß╗âm tra server</li>
            <li><code>GET /api/hrm/test</code> - Test vß╗¢i API Key</li>
            <li><code>GET /api/hrm/products</code> - Lß║Ñy danh s├ích sß║ún phß║⌐m</li>
            <li><code>POST /api/hrm/products</code> - Tß║ío sß║ún phß║⌐m</li>
            <li><code>PUT /api/hrm/products/[id]</code> - Cß║¡p nhß║¡t sß║ún phß║⌐m</li>
